{"lemma":"نَفِيسٍ","slug":"نَفِيسٍ","root":"ن.ف.س","root_slug":"ن-ف-س","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ف-س","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40265"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B3%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"precious, costly, valuable, good","examples":[{"text":"قَدَّمْتُ لَهَا هَدِيَّةً نَفِيسَةً فِي عِيدِ مِيلَادِهَا.","english":"I gave her a precious gift on her birthday."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"فَعِيل (faʕīl)-type stative-verb derived from the active participle from the verb نَفُسَ (nafusa)."},"ipa":["/na.fiːs/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40265","headword_ar":"نَفِيسٌ","root":"nfs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high in estimation; of high account; excellent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M, Msb, TA;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"highly prized; precious; valuable; and therefore"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desired with emulation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in much request;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good, goodly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellent, in its kind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAfisN","text_ar":"نَافِسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (M,) and so does ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munofisN","text_ar":"مُنْفِسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh, M, A, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manofuwsN","text_ar":"مَنْفُوسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) it signifies thus when applied to property, as well as other things; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manofisN","text_ar":"مَنْفِسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lh, M:) and, when so applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which one is avaricious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenacious:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munofisN","text_ar":"مُنْفِسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", so applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant; much;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munofasN","text_ar":"مُنْفَسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Fr, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAfisN","text_ar":"نَافِسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of high account"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"estimation, and an object of desire:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) this last is also applied, in like manner, to a man; as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafiysN","text_ar":"نَفِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and the pl. [of either] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nifaAsN","text_ar":"نِفَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA) You also say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorN manofuwsN fiyhi","text_ar":"اَمْرٌ مَنْفُوسٌ فِيهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is desired."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi","text_ar":"فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aYo'N mutanaAfasN","text_ar":"شَىْءٌ مُتَنَافَسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing emulously desired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in much request."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b2-  Also, [as an epithet in which the quality of a subst. predominates,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Much property;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munofisN","text_ar":"مُنْفِسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lifulaAnK munofisN","text_ar":"لِفُلَانٍ مُنْفِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafiysN","text_ar":"نَفِيسٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has much property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yasur~uniY bih`*aA AlA^amori manofisN","text_ar":"مَا يَسُرُّنِى بِهٰذَا الاَمْرِ مَنْفِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafiysN","text_ar":"نَفِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Much property does not rejoice me with this affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","M","Lh","A","Msb","K","Fr"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}